comments in html
use <!-- and to end a comment, you need to use -->

main tag in html
main HTML5 tag helps search engines and other developers find the main content of your page
Example
<main>
  <h1>Hello World</h1>
  <p>Hello Paragraph</p>
</main>

Linking to internal section of page using acnchor tag-->
o create an internal link, you assign a link's href attribute to a hash symbol # 
plus the value of the id attribute for the element that you want to internally link to
<a href="#contacts-header">Contacts</a>
...
<h2 id="contacts-header">Contacts</h2>

Turning an imge into link =->
ex- a href="#"><img src="https://bit.ly/fcc-running-cats" alt="Three kittens running towards the camera."></a>

form making 
to creat a box --><input/>
to create box of specifuc type
<input type="text"/>
to add a place holder input that is text that appears on the box
<input type ="text" place holder=""/>
to create a submit box-->
<button type="submit"> submit</button>
form comes under form tags 
<form action="">
</form>( action add the link of the server  to which data is to be submitted )
we can make the field required to be filled by putting required inside input tag 
<input type="text" required>



